22 September 2010 
Hi Louise
 
I am just working on a chapter for a book (US) that ostensibly relates to the needs to transform business education - I have been given the task of a summative 'rant' about what is wrong with the current approach!!! I notice that you recently delivered a keynote that probably overlaps with this theme. I wondered whether you would be happy to send me a copy / notes so that I can cross reference to this. I would also welcome any other thoughts / comments that you may have - my basic premise is that what we do is no longer fit for purpose - we are locked in time, tradition and real estate and we will soon be living with the consequences of that!
 
Many thanks
 
Professor C J Birch
Emeritus Professor (Business and Enterprise Education)
 
07753 582179
profcjbirch@gmail.com
 
 
 
 


